# Auto-resolve three-way merges of i18n translation JSON files by unioning the
# keys from both sides. Real conflicts (same key changed to different values, or
# update-vs-delete) are left with standard conflict markers for manual review.
#
# The driver itself is registered per-clone by script/setupMergeDriver.ts, which
# runs from the `prepare` npm script. See script/mergeI18nJson.ts.
packages/seed-bible/seed-bible/i18n/*.json merge=i18n-json

*.js diff
*.jsx diff
*.ts diff
*.tsx diff
*.html diff
*.css diff
*.txt diff